---
// Prototype Index - Navigate between the 5 design prototypes
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Design Prototypes | sujeet.pro</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="proto-page">
      <header class="proto-header">
        <a href="/" class="proto-back">&larr; Back to site</a>
        <h1 class="proto-title">Design Prototypes</h1>
        <p class="proto-subtitle">Five unique article page designs for sujeet.pro. Each demonstrates a three-column layout with sidebar navigation, table of contents, and responsive behavior.</p>
      </header>

      <div class="proto-grid">
        <a href="/prototypes/design-1-editorial" class="proto-card proto-card-1">
          <div class="proto-card-number">01</div>
          <h2 class="proto-card-title">Editorial Magazine</h2>
          <p class="proto-card-desc">Rich typography, generous whitespace, newspaper-inspired column layout. Playfair Display + Source Serif 4. Warm cream palette with editorial red accent.</p>
          <div class="proto-card-tags">
            <span class="proto-tag">Serif</span>
            <span class="proto-tag">Light theme</span>
            <span class="proto-tag">Drop caps</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/prototypes/design-2-ide" class="proto-card proto-card-2">
          <div class="proto-card-number">02</div>
          <h2 class="proto-card-title">Developer IDE</h2>
          <p class="proto-card-desc">Code editor aesthetic, monospace accents, dark theme. IBM Plex Mono primary. File explorer sidebar, status bar, line numbers, syntax highlighting colors.</p>
          <div class="proto-card-tags">
            <span class="proto-tag">Monospace</span>
            <span class="proto-tag">Dark theme</span>
            <span class="proto-tag">Terminal</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/prototypes/design-3-zen" class="proto-card proto-card-3">
          <div class="proto-card-number">03</div>
          <h2 class="proto-card-title">Minimalist Zen</h2>
          <p class="proto-card-desc">Ultra-clean, lots of breathing room, subtle animations. DM Sans. Pure black and white with massive whitespace. Typography is the only design element.</p>
          <div class="proto-card-tags">
            <span class="proto-tag">Sans-serif</span>
            <span class="proto-tag">Ultra-minimal</span>
            <span class="proto-tag">B&W</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/prototypes/design-4-dashboard" class="proto-card proto-card-4">
          <div class="proto-card-number">04</div>
          <h2 class="proto-card-title">Modern Dashboard</h2>
          <p class="proto-card-desc">Card-based UI, floating panels, glass morphism. Plus Jakarta Sans. Dark blue with indigo gradients, modern SaaS feel, micro-interactions.</p>
          <div class="proto-card-tags">
            <span class="proto-tag">Glass morphism</span>
            <span class="proto-tag">Dark theme</span>
            <span class="proto-tag">Gradients</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/prototypes/design-5-academic" class="proto-card proto-card-5">
          <div class="proto-card-number">05</div>
          <h2 class="proto-card-title">Academic Paper</h2>
          <p class="proto-card-desc">Scholarly typography, section numbers, margin notes. EB Garamond serif. Paper-like background, academic journal feel, footnote references.</p>
          <div class="proto-card-tags">
            <span class="proto-tag">Serif</span>
            <span class="proto-tag">Paper theme</span>
            <span class="proto-tag">Scholarly</span>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>

      <footer class="proto-footer">
        <p>Each prototype is a self-contained page with sidebar navigation, table of contents, and full article content.</p>
        <p>Click a design to view the full prototype. Use the sidebar toggles in the header to show/hide navigation and TOC.</p>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>

<style is:global>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  body {
    font-family: 'DM Sans', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
    background: #0a0a0a;
    color: #e5e5e5;
    min-height: 100vh;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  }

  .proto-page {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 60px 24px 80px;
  }

  .proto-back {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #888;
    text-decoration: none;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    transition: color 150ms;
  }
  .proto-back:hover { color: #fff; }

  .proto-header { margin-bottom: 60px; }

  .proto-title {
    font-size: clamp(36px, 5vw, 56px);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .proto-subtitle {
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #888;
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  .proto-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(min(100%, 420px), 1fr));
    gap: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }

  .proto-card {
    display: block;
    padding: 32px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    border: 1px solid #222;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 300ms cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .proto-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 300ms;
  }
  .proto-card:hover {
    border-color: #444;
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
  }
  .proto-card:hover::before { opacity: 1; }

  .proto-card-1::before { background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(181,50,42,0.08), transparent); }
  .proto-card-2::before { background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(137,180,250,0.08), transparent); }
  .proto-card-3::before { background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.04), transparent); }
  .proto-card-4::before { background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(99,102,241,0.08), transparent); }
  .proto-card-5::before { background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(107,76,59,0.08), transparent); }

  .proto-card-number {
    font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #555;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .proto-card-title {
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    position: relative;
  }

  .proto-card-desc {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #888;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .proto-card-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 8px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .proto-tag {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 500;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 99px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    color: #aaa;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  }

  .proto-card-1:hover .proto-card-title { color: #E8847E; }
  .proto-card-2:hover .proto-card-title { color: #89B4FA; }
  .proto-card-3:hover .proto-card-title { color: #fff; }
  .proto-card-4:hover .proto-card-title { color: #818CF8; }
  .proto-card-5:hover .proto-card-title { color: #C4A882; }

  .proto-footer {
    text-align: center;
    padding-top: 40px;
    border-top: 1px solid #1a1a1a;
  }
  .proto-footer p {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #555;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  :focus-visible {
    outline: 2px solid #6366F1;
    outline-offset: 2px;
  }
</style>
